<lb n="0022a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0022a2901">是法印呪。若善男子<note n="0022013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">善＝若【甲】</note><note n="0022013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善【大】，若【甲】</note><app n="0022013"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">若</rdg></app>女人等。多諸障難一
<pb n="0022b" xml:id="T19.0922.0022b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0022b01" ed="T"/>切疾病。女人難<note n="0022014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">月＝有【乙】</note><note n="0022014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月【大】，有【乙】</note><app n="0022014"><lem wit="【大】">月</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">有</rdg></app>產厄。願欲轉禍求福。并
<lb n="0022b02" ed="T"/>患鬼神病難差者。以五色線搓索。呪繫病人
<lb n="0022b03" ed="T"/>項及手足腰腹等。仍須請七僧。建置道場造
<lb n="0022b04" ed="T"/>本尊像。寫藥師經六時行道。燃七層<note n="0022015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">燈＝燃【乙】</note><note n="0022015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">燈【大】，燃【乙】</note><app n="0022015"><lem wit="【大】">燈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">燃</rdg></app>。造
<lb n="0022b05" ed="T"/>五色幡四十九尺。日轉經四十九遍。放水陸
<lb n="0022b06" ed="T"/>生命四十九頭。時花<note n="0022016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔菓子〕－【乙】</note><note n="0022016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菓子【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0022016"><lem wit="【大】">菓子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>殷勤供養。呪五色
<lb n="0022b07" ed="T"/>線發願。又以印拄於線上。更呪四十九遍。結
<lb n="0022b08" ed="T"/>四十九結。復念此真言。加持真言曰。</p>
